kubectl describe pods mypod  - get pods status
kubectl get all   - get all information
kubectl delete pods mypod  - delete pod
kubectl port-forward mypod 8080:80  - external ports
kubectl proxy - public API
kubectl logs mypod -c mycontainer -f - logs of the CONTAINER
kubectl exec -it mypod sh - enter to pod
kubectl delete all -all  - delete all pods 
kubectl get pods -n kube-system  - get all namespaces


YML
requests - minimum thet is needed to start
limits - max amount that is needed